1. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper deals with modeling the spread of rumors and diseases in a social network, which falls under the purview of social and information networks. 
2. cs.SD (Software Engineering) - The paper proposes an estimator for identifying the infection source, which can be seen as a software engineering problem. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with controlling the spread of infections in a network, which can be seen as a systems and control problem. 
4. cs.SN (Social and Information Networks) - Similar to point 1, the paper deals with modeling the spread of rumors and diseases in a social network. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes an algorithmic approach for identifying the infection source, which can be seen as a data structures and algorithms problem.
